Uses of Package
asteroids.game

  • Packages that use asteroids.game 
    Package Description
    asteroids.game
    This package contains the high-level classes that coordinate the appearance and operation of the game.
    asteroids.participants
    All of the classes in this package extend the abstract Participant class to define a new kind of participant in the game.
  • Classes in asteroids.game used by asteroids.game 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Controls a game of Asteroids.
    Display
    Defines the top-level appearance of an Asteroids game.
    Participant
    Represents a single moving element in an asteroids game.
    ParticipantState
    Keeps track of the Participants, their motions, and their collisions.
    Screen
    The area of the display in which the game takes place.
  • Classes in asteroids.game used by asteroids.participants 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Controls a game of Asteroids.
    Participant
    Represents a single moving element in an asteroids game.
